**Next chapter:** The Concerto — Rachmaninoff Piano Concerto No. 2, Op. 18. We orchestrate, voice, and conduct the full first movement (exposition) — section voices (GAP-6), expressive timing (rubato, Ch13), full harmonic voicing (Ch6), and the form we just learned. It's the summit.

